name: Furry Rag Kitten
description: oooh! VERY cuddly and EXTRA cute Furry Rag Kitten in light gingery coloured man made furry fabric. This fella is approx 16 inches tall and has a lovely SMILEY face which is hand embroidered and so are his paws. He has orange spotty buttons and orange ribbons, a golden bell that jingles and a gingery coloured woollen tail that is plaited and tied with a matching orange ribbon. He is stuffed with 100% hollow fibre polyester filling. Super CUTE! You gotta love this kitten!

name: Skanky Rag Cat
description: Skanky Rag Cats are a bit skanky but very lovable! They are made with 100% black cotton with white cotton patches on their ears, bodies, arms, legs and feet. Skanky fellas have a 'dead eye' and a button for the other eye, they have hand embroidered faces and paws, a ribbon, a shiny bell, buttons on their bellies and a black woollen plaited tail tied with ribbon. They are 22 inches tall and stuffed with 100% hollow fibre polyester filling. Give one a home!

name: Gingham Rag Cat
description: Gorgeous Gingham Rag Cats are available in 100% cotton. Happy smiley hand embroidered face and paws, buttons, ribbons, a shiny jingling bell and a woollen tail plaited and tied with ribbon. These lovely kitties are approx 22 inches tall and are stuffed with 100% soft and snuggly hollow fibre polyester filling. Available in several colours with co-ordinated buttons and ribbons!

name: Fleecey Rag Rabbit
description: Soft and cuddly Rag Rabbit made of pink and white spotted fleecey fabric. This beautiful bunny has a hand embroidered face and paws, floppy ears, a pink and white ribbon bow around his neck, a shiny jingling silver bell and pink and white spotty buttons on his tum. He has a white woollen pom pom tail and is approx 22 inches tall. Stuffed with very soft 100% hoolow fibre polyester filling.

name: Fleecey Rag Cat
description: Lovely, happy, cuddly, snuggly, fleecey Rag Cat in pink and white spotty fleece fabric. This fella has a hand embroidered face and paws, a pink and white spotty ribbon, matching buttons, a shiny jingling bell and a white woollen tail which is plaited and tied with a ribbon. He is approx 22 inches tall and is stuffed with very soft 100% hollow fibre polyester filling. Give him a hug! Give him a home!
